bs-interwikisearch-label: Label for the interwiki search panel
bs-interwikisearch-item-button-label:
Label message for the results from other wikis.
$1 - wiki name, $2 - number of hits
bs-interwikisearch-results-dialog-title: Title for the dialog containing results from other wikis
bs-interwikisearch-results-dialog-button: Label for the button that opens target wiki's search page
Label for the button that closes the target wiki's result dialog
bs-interwikisearch-error-generic:
Generic error message if target wiki did not specify error message.
$1 - target name
bs-interwikisearch-error-generic-with-me:
Generic error message if target wiki specifier error message.
$1 - target name, $2 - error message
bs-interwikisearch-error-open-target-act: Button label to switch to target wiki
bs-interwikisearch-error-open-login-acti: Button label to login on target wiki
bs-interwikisearch-redirect-suggestion-l: Message displayed to the user when error response indicates problem will not be solved by logging into the target wiki
bs-interwikisearch-results-desc-label: Help message for other wiki's result dialog
